      • Property Summary

        Properties 
        Name Description
        DocLimitations
        Used to indicate any limitations on the document (e.g. as a person may only be allowed to spend a max of 30 days in country on a visitor's visa).
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:String_Short
        Example Value I am a short string.
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 9
        AdditionalName
        The name of an additional person listed on this document.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:String_Short
        Example Value I am a short string.
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 100
        EffectiveExpireDate
        The effective and expiry date of the document.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:Date_EffectiveExpire
        Example Value ???
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        Privacy
        Allows for control of the sharing of document data between parties.
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:Privacy
        Example Value ???
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        DocType
        Indicates the type of document (e.g. Passport, Military ID, Drivers License, national ID, Vaccination Certificate). Refer to OpenTravel Code List Document Type (DOC).
        Details
        Type http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v0:DocumentType_Enum
        Example Value NaturalizationCertificate
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
